rmp.university: University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill
comments: Isn't really helpful. Dr. Parke is a really nice guy but his teaching is so inadequate that you have to teach yourself everything. Tests are confusing and he grades harshly. Do not take his class unless you are very good at math.
The professor was a little hard to follow but the class was easy enough.  This is the easiest professor for 570, with the best grading distribution. The tests are pretty straightforward.
